<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/57201AVHSVBLCRCLQGNRQCCGBRSLVVRBN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Community Jam";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Community Jam</h1><h2>FREE Monthly Improv Jam</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Time:</span> 3:30pm – 5:30pm<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Ages:</span> 19+<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Level Required:</span> no improv experience is required!<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Cost:</span> FREE with registration<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Max 2 enrollments per email, per jam</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Have a craving for the stage? Come and improvise with professionally trained performers at our free community jam session where you can walk up, drop in, and learn from the pros. If you’ve been itching to get involved in the improv community, this is for you!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>LOCK OUT POLICY:<span><br/></span>Doors will lock 15 minutes after the class begins. Late comers will not be permitted.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>WAITLIST:<span><br/></span>If a class is sold out for a date you're hoping to attend, you can write in to <span class=\"BoldText\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"mailto:boxoffice@theimprovcentre.ca\">boxoffice@theimprovcentre.ca</a></span> to be added to a waitlist. While TIC can't guarantee you'll get a spot, we'll reach out if we can fit you in the class.
""";
