<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/60201ANRDGSBSTNSDPCQLQLGLJPGGMRSQ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Spontaneous Combustion";
  schema:description """
	<h2>Tuesdays, once a month!</h2><span><br/></span>Step into our improv laboratory as Mainstage veterans team up with the friendly faces from our House Teams for a night of unpredictable comedy. In the spirit of a Pro-Am comedy show, this experimental blend of seasoned pros and rising stars creates the perfect comedic concoction. <span><br/></span> <span><br/></span>With mixed experience levels and zero safety goggles, expect a hilarious chain reaction of improv scenes where anything can happen. Get ready to witness comedy in its rawest, most reactive form! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets are Sliding Scale: $10-$15-$20<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Run time: 90 minutes including intermission<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: 🌶️🌶️ – Content is cheeky, playful, some innuendo is possible. Think “Shrek” level content. Best for audiences age 8 and up. (PG)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All physical vouchers must now be redeemed via phone or email. Please contact the box office for assistance.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-07-14T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/files/f4c5bbe9-02e3-403f-957b-d0e44f887b34.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/location/603AMBLCJQMLRJDMDQKBNHDKQPPDPCQLJ>;
  schema:organizer <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/organization/the-improv-centre>;
  schema:url <https://theimprovcentre.ca/shows/>;
