  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Summer Weekend Matinee Series";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Break up your summer day with a side-splitting improv matinee!</h1><span><br/></span><h2>Summer Weekend Matinee Series</h2>Looking for fun family activities in Vancouver this summer? Spend an afternoon at <span class=\"BoldText\">The Improv Centre</span> on Granville Island with our <span class=\"BoldText\">Summer Weekend Matinee Series</span>. Featuring a rotating lineup of hilarious, family-friendly improv comedy, these 90-minute shows are the perfect addition to your Granville Island adventure. Escape the summer heat in cool A/C, enjoy plenty of laughs, then head back out to explore the island’s shops, markets, waterfront, and attractions.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether you're visiting Granville Island for the first time, entertaining out-of-town guests, or searching for fun weekend activities for kids, teens, and adults alike, our Summer Weekend Matinee Series offers something for everyone.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>TIC Summer Games</h2>Get ready for some friendly competition! Two teams of improvisers face off in a series of fast-paced comedy challenges inspired by your suggestions. Packed with audience interaction, quick wit, and non-stop laughs, this special matinee-only show is a family-friendly pick that’s perfect for all ages.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Blockbuster</h2>Lights, camera, laughter! Your suggestions inspire an entirely original movie created live on stage. From action adventures and superhero epics to hilarious romances and unexpected plot twists, every performance is completely unique. It’s one of the most entertaining things to do on Granville Island this summer.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>True Story!</h2>Every great story starts with a true one. Audience members shares a real-life experiences, and our cast transforms it into heartfelt and hilarious improvised comedy. In the second half, our performers share some stories of their own, leading to hilarious real-life laughs. Filled with unexpected and genuine moments, <span class=\"BoldText\">True Story!</span> is a one-of-a-kind live comedy experience.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Relaxed Performance – True Story, July 25th</span><span><br/></span>This selected performance of <span class=\"BoldText\">True Story</span> is offered as a Relaxed Performance. We create a welcoming theatre experience for audience members with reduced sensory stimulation where possible, a supportive atmosphere, and the freedom to leave and re-enter the theatre as needed.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>These Relaxed Performances also feature <span class=\"BoldText\">sliding scale tickets ($10, $15, or $20)</span>, helping make live theatre more accessible for families and community members looking for affordable things to do in Vancouver.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.theimprovcentre.ca/relaxed-performances/\">Click here to learn more about Relaxed Performances</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Run time: 90 minutes with one 15 minute intermission.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: 🌶️ – Suitable for all audiences. Children are required to attend with a caregiver. (G)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All physical vouchers must now be redeemed via phone or email. Please contact the box office for assistance.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-08-22T14:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/files/9b076a12-1dda-422f-bbfe-90ab843a9b68.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/location/603AMBLCJQMLRJDMDQKBNHDKQPPDPCQLJ>;
