ected and genuine moments, <span class=\"BoldText\">True Story!</span> is a one-of-a-kind live comedy experience.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Relaxed Performance – True Story, July 25th</span><span><br/></span>This selected performance of <span class=\"BoldText\">True Story</span> is offered as a Relaxed Performance. We create a welcoming theatre experience for audience members with reduced sensory stimulation where possible, a supportive atmosphere, and the freedom to leave and re-enter the theatre as needed.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>These Relaxed Performances also feature <span class=\"BoldText\">sliding scale tickets ($10, $15, or $20)</span>, helping make live theatre more accessible for families and community members looking for affordable things to do in Vancouver.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.theimprovcentre.ca/relaxed-performances/\">Click here to learn more about Relaxed Performances</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Run time: 90 minutes with one 15 minute intermission.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: 🌶️ – Suitable for all audiences. Children are required to attend with a caregiver. (G)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All physical vouchers must now be redeemed via phone or email. Please contact the box office for assistance.
